Radio &quot;retreat&quot; on the Queen Mary in January had one of your boxes 
with him and was trying to demonstrate it to me but apparently the 
battery case shorted in some fashion and the holder partially Melted 
(Randy Schneider).

I&#39;ve done a fair amount of research into the history of EVP (I prefer 
to call it PSP or Paranormal Sound Phenomena as there are 
unexplainable sounds besides voices captured AND I even have copies 
of &quot;spirit voices&quot; that were recorded via non-electronic means).

I&#39;ve kept my (almost a full year) correspondence with Alec to be only 
with respect to the Intelligence Project as I know he&#39;s been pretty 
busy. But I just got an e-mail from him a few days about another 
project he&#39;s working on which I&#39;ll tell everyone here about in a day 
or two.

Guy

